extendedInfo.description: Take a photo and find your celebrity look alike from over 100,000 celebrities. Find out whether you look like Brad or Angelina and share with your friends :-)Features:* Take a photo or select one from your gallery, and our face recognition engine will find your celebrity look alikes* Share your matches with friends on Facebook, Twitter, Buzz or MySpace* Rate other matches and write funny comments about them* Check out ratings and comments on your own matchesFor best results:* Take photos in good lighting conditions* Use frontal photos* Remove eyeglasses/sunglasses* Smile!

reviews.title: Totally inconsistent
reviews.comment: Essentially it just matches to a celeb with a similar hairstyle. I uploaded 4 pics, it couldn\'t match one, another was matched to Miley Cyrus (long wavy hair, no fringe) and the other two to Katie Holmes and Naomi Campbell (both with blunt fringe hairstyles similar to my current do). I don\'t look like any of them...
reviews.author: Jennifer Rham
